{"tid":1967442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實捉鬼撚鬥黃撚捉偽黃撚只係一班自私既人","createTime":"2020-04-11T02:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T16:14:31.000Z","uid":199727,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf05fa1b177f51649509aaec36fa91e82048491a","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"首先，我問你地一個前線勇武，同一個ig fb repost文宣加食黃店打卡既和理非邊個黃啲?<br />\n如無意外，前線勇武當然係黃啲啦，因為佢地為自己既理念甚至捨棄自己前途。<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問，你地有幾可會見到勇武不斷喺連登屌柒和理非? 好少，因為和勇不分已經係勇武既潛意識。佢地明白和理非都有佢地既難處。就算佢地唔能夠付出更多，企得更前，勇武都仍然企係到，為抗爭默默貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n咁和理非呢? 一直以來，連登持續都出現捉鬼捉五毛捉網軍捉pr公司捉鬼捉偽黃鬥黃捉中立，邊個食m記邊個玩騰訊暴雪game係偽黃係死支那仔。 呢一班懶醒既人往往唔知佢地既標籤行為會破壞黃營團結。呢啲標籤行為只會令佢地自己產生優越感，「傻閪我唔玩LoL架，我唔食M記架，所以我黃過你!」但實質完全唔會有任何貢獻。有幾多人真係會因為你地屌鳩佢所以改變佢地消費既決定? 由頭到尾都係你地班標籤撚自high咋。 <br />\n<br />\n我身邊既勇武朋友見到連登最近既風氣真係笑而不語。一班唔願意付出更多既連登和理非竟然喺網上同人鬥黃，如果繼續鬥黃鬥落去既話，不如擇個日子去MK鬥用火魔仲實際啦，好無?"},{"pid":"5d080ba579ce9606da08dd110b3f8c32e93d68cc","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"核彈"},{"pid":"147f83732521853f3b6c069076f3362e3890ba36","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"4b43da3514fdf7509ca91e55811af25b2e92af3d","tid":1967442,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"兒登仔係咁架啦"},{"pid":"0a5a1fc00347fd56070ccf879f7f3f80350887df","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b43da3514fdf7509ca91e55811af25b2e92af3d","tid":1967442,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"兒登仔係咁架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"對佢地實在太失望 好多人俾佢地帶哂風向"},{"pid":"0c32027701f6966ccca4f31210ab0282dca34050","tid":1967442,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:56:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有鬼唔捉咪變今日嘅泛民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d50c8145ffadfe4c54a969ac19dc9ad89fefe90e","tid":1967442,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"189fa6edfb73439d8465b3f31d6b426458fd43f7","tid":1967442,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0a5a1fc00347fd56070ccf879f7f3f80350887df","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b43da3514fdf7509ca91e55811af25b2e92af3d","tid":1967442,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"兒登仔係咁架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"對佢地實在太失望 好多人俾佢地帶哂風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋上Twitter 做野，屌返我假膠<br />\nexcuse me?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2675551b93677ed06a672bb20d5e4c88fe33ee","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f4211a38903f529a94a75389d5bd20a2c52ebf5b","tid":1967442,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"推，成班兒登仔"},{"pid":"ed879e6abb6fe2ef59f556b85a9dd8824553504c","tid":1967442,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:05:29.000Z","msg":"標籤行為得一個黨會做，就係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而網上鬥黃只係共狗作故仔分化既把戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落到場根本未見過人鬥黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用言語去分化，用標籤去矮化。不過連登仔都唔係傻仔黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fdf3887fb76647210b72a5ee27ea86d07237d3","tid":1967442,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"c91060696bcfaed4bc40713a54a259e7183600